<style>
.menu-highlight .elementor-icon-list-item.active .elementor-icon-list-text,
.menu-highlight .elementor-icon-list-item.active .elementor-icon-list-icon i{
    color: #FACA22;
}
</style>
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
<script>

var className = 'menu-highlight',
    $ =jQuery,
    clickLock = false

$(document).ready(function(){

$('.' + className + ' .elementor-icon-list-item').on('click', function(){
    $('.' + className + ' .elementor-icon-list-item').removeClass('active')
    $(this).addClass('active')
    clickLock = true
    setTimeout(function(){
        clickLock = false
    },500)
})
})

$(window).on('load scroll', function(){
    
    if( clickLock ) return
    
    var ids = [],
        id
    
    $('.elementor-top-section, [data-elementor-type="wp-page"] > .e-con, [data-elementor-type="wp-page"] > .e-container').each(function(){
        if($(window).scrollTop() + $(window).height() - 350 > $(this).offset().top){
            ids.push($(this).attr('id'))
        }
    })
    
    ids = ids.filter(element => {
      return element !== undefined
    })
    
    id = ids[ids.length - 1]
    
    $('.elementor-icon-list-item').removeClass('active')
    $('[href="#'+id+'"]').parent().addClass('active')
})

</script>

<style>
body,html{
    overflow-x: hidden !important;
}
.service-box:hover .service-icon .elementor-icon-box-icon .elementor-icon{
    background: #ffffff;
    
}
.service-box:hover{
    background: #FACA22 !important;
}
.service-icon .elementor-icon-box-icon .elementor-icon{
    background: #f5f7ff;
    height: 65px;
    width: 65px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transition: all .3s;
}


.testimonial-area .elementskit-commentor-header{
    text-align: center !important;
}

.progress-bar .eael-progressbar-title,.progress-bar .eael-progressbar-count-wrap{
    margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.progress-bar .eael-progressbar-line{
    border-radius: 5px;    
}
.progress-bar .eael-progressbar-line-fill{
    border-radius: 5px 0px 0px 5px;  
}





.scroll-down-arrow {
    -webkit-animation: mover 3s infinite  alternate;
    animation: mover 3s infinite  alternate;
}
.scroll-down-arrow {
    -webkit-animation: mover 3s infinite  alternate;
    animation: mover 3s infinite  alternate;
}
@-webkit-keyframes mover {
    0% { transform: translateY(0); }
    100% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
}
@keyframes mover {
    0% { transform: translateY(0); }
    100% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
}





/*background Animation*/


.animated-line {
    animation: bg-animation-1 5s ease-out infinite;
    height: 20px;
}
.animation-line-2{
    animation: bg-animation-2 5s ease-out infinite;
    height: 20px;
}
.animation-line-3{
    animation: bg-animation-1 10s ease-out infinite;
    height: 20px;
}
.animation-line-4{
    animation: bg-animation-2 10s ease-out infinite;
    height: 20px;
}

@keyframes bg-animation-1 {
  0% {
    top: 0px;
    opacity: 1;
  }
  50% {
    top: 50%;
    opacity: .5;	
  }
  100% {
    top: 100%;
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
@keyframes bg-animation-2 {
  0% {
    opacity: 1;
    bottom: 0px;
  }
  50% {
    bottom: 50%;
    opacity: .5;	
  }
  100% {
    bottom: 100%;
    opacity: 1;
  }
}










.close-icon,.nav-icon{
    cursor: pointer;
}

[data-elementor-type="wp-page"] > .e-con:not(.sidebar-section),
[data-elementor-type="wp-page"] > .elementor-section-wrap > .e-con:not(.sidebar-section){
    margin-left: 210px !important;
    width: calc(100% - 210px) !important;
}
@media only screen and (max-width: 1199px) {
    .elementor-top-section{
        margin-left:0;
    }
}
.elementor-top-section{
    position: fixed;
    width: 210px;
}
@media only screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
    [data-elementor-type="wp-page"] > .e-con:not(.sidebar-section),
    [data-elementor-type="wp-page"] > .elementor-section-wrap > .e-con:not(.sidebar-section){
    margin-left: 0px !important;
    width: 100% !important;
}
    .elementor-top-section{
    overflow-y: scroll;
    margin-left: -250px;
    transition: all .3s;
    }
    .elementor-top-section.side-show{
        margin-left: 0px !important;
    }
}
</style>


<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.1/jquery.min.js"></script>


<script>
$(document).ready(function(){
  $(".nav-icon").click(function(){
    $(".elementor-top-section").addClass("side-show");
  });
  $(".close-icon").click(function(){
    $(".elementor-top-section").removeClass("side-show");
  });
});


</script>
